<h2> Definition </h2>

<p>
<strong>@HI{{kamo shiremasenn}}</strong> expresses the speaker's conjecture, possibly from some information he has. Note, however, 
that the probability that the conjecture is correct is lower than with @HI{{deshou}}.
</p>

